data.description: Welcome Home to beautiful waterfront community of Walden on Lake Conroe! Immaculate, affordable, & gorgeous inside. Well maintained townhome offers spacious floorplan, open high ceilings, gas/wood fireplace, tile/wood & carpeted floors, granite counters, stainless appliances, picture rail wall in dining room, & main suite offers private balcony, walk-in closet, double sinks & tile shower. Flexible living & dining areas are a true entertainer's delight. In addition to light, bright this home offers a wonderful outdoor gazebo w/private fenced yard within a tranquil resort setting. LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION...Near Fitness Center, Tennis Courts, Boat Ramp, & beautiful Lake Conroe! Incomparable resort-living at its finest in the highly acclaimed area of Walden featuring Golf Course, full-service marina, Yacht Club dining, lakeside pool, two boat ramps, parks, trails, and deer in your yard. Low monthly yard/trash maintenance fees.
